# =============================================================================
# 目标：仓库只保留「可复制的配置 + 文档 + 技能源码」，不保留下载产物与密钥。
# 若曾误提交大目录，改完 ignore 后需执行（一次即可）：
#   git rm -r --cached workspace/.cache workspace/.local workspace/node_modules workspace/.npm
#   git commit -m "chore: stop tracking workspace build caches"
# =============================================================================

# --- 密钥与本地环境（可复制时用 *.example 代替）---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
org/local.env
org/volc-api.env
settings/

# --- OpenClaw 主 workspace：语言运行时、包管理器、浏览器缓存（体积极大）---
workspace/.local/
workspace/.cache/
workspace/.npm/
workspace/node_modules/

# 其它 workspace-* 子岗（若日后在仓库内装依赖，同规则生效）
workspace-*/.local/
workspace-*/.cache/
workspace-*/.npm/
workspace-*/node_modules/

# --- 任意路径下的依赖与虚拟环境（技能、脚本子项目）---
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
.venv/
pip-wheel-metadata/
*.egg-info/

# --- 本机托管浏览器配置（Chrome profile 等）---
browser/

# --- 媒体与临时大包（按需保留示例小文件即可）---
memory/
media/
*.mp4
*.webm
*.mov
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# --- Python ---
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.Python

# --- 日志与运行态 ---
*.log
logs/
update-check.json
exec-approvals.json
**/.perf_last_notify

# --- OpenClaw 配置里常含密钥：用示例文件进库 ---
openclaw.json
openclaw.json.bak
openclaw.json.bak.*

# --- 设备与凭证目录 ---
credentials/
devices/
identity/
feishu/dedup/
sandboxes/
org/backups/
org/.perf_last_notify
auth-profiles.json
agents/*/agent/auth-profiles.json

# --- 会话与长 transcript（体积极大）---
agents/*/sessions/
**/*.jsonl
**/*.jsonl.reset.*
**/.openclaw/workspace-state.json

# --- 嵌套 git / 个人记忆（不随组织仓库复制）---
workspace/.git/
workspace/MEMORY.md
workspace/memory/

# --- 杂项 ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
cron/jobs.json.bak
